ard%20(Genus%20I%2C%20Genus%20II%2C%20Baby%20Boomer%2C%20Young%0APlayers)%20and%20the%20format%20was%20a%20hit%2C%20the%20cocktail-cabinet%20with%20four%0Acolored%20category%20buttons%20was%20in%20bars%20across%20America.%20The%20%3Cem%3EAll%20Star%0ASports%3C%2Fem%3E%20edition%20was%20the%20last%20one%20out%20the%20door%20that%20spring%20and%20the%0Aonly%20one%20targeted%20at%20a%20specific%20demographic%3A%20every%20category%2C%20every%0Aquestion%2C%20every%20answer%20was%20about%20sports.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20the%20era%20when%20sports%20bar%20culture%20had%20just%20fused%20with%0Acoin-op%2C%20you%E2%80%99d%20sit%20down%20at%20the%20Trivial%20Pursuit%20table%20between%0Ainnings%20of%20the%20Sox%20game%2C%20while%20the%20jukebox%20played%20Springsteen%E2%80%99s%0A%3Cem%3EBorn%20in%20the%20U.S.A.%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20try%20to%20remember%20who%20won%20the%201962%20World%0ASeries.%20All%20Star%20Sports%20was%20designed%20to%20be%20%3Cem%3Ethe%3C%2Fem%3E%20machine%20for%20that%0Abar%3A%20if%20you%20walked%20up%20and%20saw%20its%20category%20wheel%2C%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20going%0Ato%20ask%20you%20about%20Shakespeare.%20Bally%20Sente%20partnered%20with%20Horn%20Abbot%0Aon%20a%20sports-only%20question%20pack%2C%20900-ish%20questions%20covering%0Abaseball%2C%20football%2C%20basketball%2C%20hockey%2C%20golf%2C%20Olympics%2C%20and%0A%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20sports%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20shipped%20it%20in%20a%20new%20cabinet%20variant%20aimed%0Asquarely%20at%20the%20tavern%20circuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20id%3D%22the-data%22%3EThe%20Data%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20897%20sports%20records%20browse%20at%0A%3Cstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fquiz.toys%2Farchive%2Fbrowse%3Fsource%3Dbally_triviasp%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%20rel%3D%22noopener%22%3E%2Fbrowse%3Fsource%3Dbally_triviasp%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%0Aheavy%20on%20boxing%2C%20horse%20racing%2C%20hockey%2C%20and%20Olympic%20trivia.%20West%0AGermany%20still%20exists.%20The%20Soviet%20Union%20competes.%20Muhammad%20Ali%20is%0Astill%20boxing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20id%3D%22how-we-cracked-it%22%3EHow%20We%20Cracked%20It%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%20id%3D%22the-question%22%3EThe%20Question%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20other%20Trivial%20Pursuit%20edition%20we%E2%80%99d%20cracked%2C%20Genus%20I%2C%20Genus%0AII%2C%20Baby%20Boomer%2C%20Young%20Players%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fquiz.toys%2Farchive%2Fposts%2Fcracking-bally-sente%2F%22%20target%3D%22_blank%22%20rel%3D%22noopener%22%3Eshared%20a%20clean%20ROM%20layout%3C%2Fa%3E%0A%3A%0AAB%20chips%20hold%20base-40%20encoded%20text%2C%20CD%20chips%20hold%20pointer%20tables%2C%0Aand%20one%20extractor%20runs%20the%20lot.%20Same%20base-40%20alphabet.%20Same%206809%20CPU.%0ASame%20hardware%20as%20the%20SAC-1%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20All%20Star%20Sports%20edition%20breaks%20the%20pattern.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20id%3D%22what-changed%22%3EWhat%20Changed%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3ESame%20base-40%20encoding.%20Same%206809%20CPU.%20Same%20hardware.%20But%20the%20ROM%20chips%20are%0Areorganized%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EText%20data%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ccode%3Eallsport.8a%3C%2Fcode%3E%20through%20%3Ccode%3Eallsport.5a%3C%2Fcode%3E%2C%20four%2016KB%20chips%20mapped%0Aat%20%3Ccode%3E%240000%3C%2Fcode%3E%2C%20%3Ccode%3E%244000%3C%2Fcode%3E%2C%20%3Ccode%3E%248000%3C%2Fcode%3E%2C%20%3Ccode%3E%24C000%3C%2Fcode%3E.%20The%20other%20editions%20use%20%3Ccode%3Eab01.bin%3C%2Fcode%3E%0Athrough%20%3Ccode%3Eab67.bin%3C%2Fcode%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPointer%20table%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20%3Ccode%3Eallsport.3a%3C%2Fcode%3E%2C%20a%20single%2016KB%20chip%20holding%20both%20the%0Aquestion%20table%20(at%20offset%20%3Ccode%3E%240000%3C%2Fcode%3E)%20and%20the%20answer%20table%20(at%20offset%20%3Ccode%3E%242000%3C%2Fcode%3E).%0AThe%20other%20editions%20use%20a%20separate%20CD%20ROM%20pair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrefix%20phrases%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Stored%20at%20%3Ccode%3E%24C000%2B%3C%2Fcode%3E%20in%20the%20text%20data%2